    "Inverse problemsAs for inverse problems in the space-time approaches (Paragraph 2.2.1.2), the non-linear operator N can be learned.",
    "For temporal problems, this corresponds to the right-hand side of Eq.",
    "( 3) for PDEs and to Eq.",
    "( 4) for systems of ODEs.",
    "The predicted right-hand side can then be used to predict time series using a classical time-stepping scheme, as proposed in [331]."
